{"tid":1596263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑評 林鄭「社區對話」","createTime":"2019-09-26T12:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:11:26.000Z","uid":51620,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a75cc6cb557930c91f0fe45d2f54ea8047dbbb83","tid":1596263,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"林鄭「社區對話」，未開始先導致：<br />\n1，鄧肇堅醫院門診部下午提早關閉；<br />\n2，鄧志昂專科醫院母嬰診所提早關門；<br />\n3，貝夫人健康院提早關閉；<br />\n4，摩利臣山泳池提早關閉。<br />\n5，幾條街多間商店包括果汁店提早關門。<br />\n<br />\n市民健康和商號先蒙受損失。<br />\n市民問得實切，特首空話連篇。<br />\n<br />\n她聲稱捍衛「一國兩制」。但只問一條：當香港國泰航空公司二百多名工作人員，因為在公餘的社交媒體發表對香港反送中風暴的觀感，中國向國泰施壓，未經審判定罪，不予提供解釋，全部予以解聘。<br />\n<br />\n解聘行動還在擴大。<br />\n<br />\n請問林鄭：你身為特首，有沒有為國泰航空公司這二百多香港員工，向中國政府力陳請命，捍衛一國兩制之下的言論生活自由，令這二百多名員工（其中許多是空姐）可以復職？還是，你可以想像她的答案：「這是個別企業機構的行政決定，政府不方便發表評論」？<br />\n<br />\n他們不再受到迫害，香港社會已經由此可以變得更好。<br />\n<br />\n連為這二百名香港納稅人，也沒有伸張常識公義，閣下憑何令人相信有能力、有誠意捍衛這個七百萬人口的大都市的法治和人權？<br />\n<br />\n三個多月過去，你還相信這個灰色物體（Grey Object ) 嗎？"},{"pid":"68f6aff690176d2a6dfc000c1aa315ed4ec46421","tid":1596263,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超直線"},{"pid":"7d480f28c2fea206c1bda9861a74349f0f993d7d","tid":1596263,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"比yellow object撚著左依家日日都提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f183c2539a50e75f1d0eb83bf9b2965e86ce68e9","tid":1596263,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f6aff690176d2a6dfc000c1aa315ed4ec46421","tid":1596263,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超直線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b7911060521add71381df34c97267235f5462","tid":1596263,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d480f28c2fea206c1bda9861a74349f0f993d7d","tid":1596263,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"比yellow object撚著左依家日日都提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就好似 &quot;我討厭政治&quot;一樣"},{"pid":"765874f18e15bbbcdccb27820c4059b274a90ca3","tid":1596263,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b313934a61404d75390ecb952cf5112e6d581ec","tid":1596263,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"926b90be6c88081b33c3d60cc2b09ab0aa2572ac","tid":1596263,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"今晚一定要聽光明頂"},{"pid":"6af724f91240339f4a5d3a1ae0a1d456d9e6fb09","tid":1596263,"uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb451cc725ccd79ebeec8b6bb6ec17454db0c6f6","tid":1596263,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"19直線, 好火滾咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f828b503e86395e9f12201e180fd7efa93dcde","tid":1596263,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"926b90be6c88081b33c3d60cc2b09ab0aa2572ac","tid":1596263,"uid":208940,"like":0,"disl